I '''Henry Alfred Kissinger''' (mibait Mayo 27, 1923) {{pron-en|ˈkɪsɪndʒər}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/Kissinger |title=Kissinger - Definition from the Merriam-Webster Online Dictionary |publisher=Merriam-Webster|accessdate=2009-10-23}}</ref>, metung yang cientistang pampulitica, diplomaticu, ampong tinanggap king [[:en:Nobel Peace Prize|Nobel Peace Prize]] a Americanung mibait king [[Alemania]]. Migsilbi ya antimong [[:en:United States National Security Advisor|National Security Advisor]] (Talausuk king Kapanatagang Pambansa) at kaibat, kayabe na niti, antimong [[:en:United States Secretary of State|Secretary of State]] (Kalihim ning Estado) king [[:en:Richard Nixon|Kapamahalang Nixon]]. Kaibat ning kayang pamanungkulan, kukunan de pa murin deng pamuntuk o presidenti ing kayang pamalak.     

Metung yang talatuki ning ''[[Realpolitik]]'' i Kissinger, a dominanti papil king [[:en:United States foreign policy|patakaran nang panlual ning America]] manibat 1969 anggang 1977. Aniang panaun a iti, ya ing misulung king patakaran ning ''[[:en:détente|détente]]'', at penigobran ne ing metung a pamitucnang-acbung (''ceasefire'') king [[:en:Vietnam War|Gerang Vietnam]].  

Angga ngeni, pupurian de i Kissinger deng kayang kayabe king profesion.<ref>Agpang king press release a pepalual ning 45th [[Munich Conference on Security Policy]] aniang Febrero 8, 2009, ''"[H]is voice continues to bear weight and authority throughout the globe."'' lon ya ing [http://www.securityconference.de/konferenzen/2009/ewald_von_kleist_preis.php?sprache=en&]Munich Security Conference - 6th February 2009 Press Release</ref>. Mirinan yang galal antimong mumunang tinanggap king Ewald von Kleist Award ning [[:en:Munich Conference on Security Policy|Munich Conference on Security Policy]] (Pulung king Patakaran a Pangkapanatagan king Munich), at magsilbi ya king salukuyan antimong talapamuntuk (''chairman'') ning [[Kissinger Associates]], metung a cumpaniang internacional king pamagunsulta (''international consulting firm''). I Kissinger ing "most frequent visitor" (pekamaralas a dalo) king [[George W. Bush]] [[White House]] antimong e oficial a talausuk a pampulitica king [[Israel]] ampong [[:en:Middle East|Kalibudtang Aslagan]] (''Middle East'')—kayabe ya ing [[:en:Invasion of Iraq|pamaglusub]] ampong [[:en:occupation of Iraq|pamaniakup king Iraq]].  

